Self-esteem is made up of thoughts, feelings and opinions we have about ourselves. It can change, depending on the way we think. Sometimes people do not realize that they are thinking negative about themselves. However, once they are aware of it, then you can begin the way you think. Some tips that I can share from my own lifetime experience
Focus on what goes well for you by being positive and thinking about yourself
Aim for the effort rather than the perfection
View mistakes as learning opportunity, meaning accept that you will make mistakes, no one is perfect in life!
Try new things and give yourself credit 
Exercise: by being active and fit it helps you feel good about yourself 
Always realize what you can change and what you cannot change 
If you use some of these tips it might help you change the way you think about yourself. Have a great day friends! SNAPCHAT alansari100 👻 #SelfEsteem #GoalsInLife #MyDubai 📸 @curlywurly_photo
